The room features white walls with gold trim, a marble fireplace with gold accents, and a portrait hanging above it. To the left is a dark wood staircase with intricate metal railings. In the center, there are two plush white armchairs and a small table with a chessboard. Ornate gold-framed mirrors and console tables are visible against the walls. A doorway leads to another room in the background. A white object, possibly a sculpture or piece of furniture, is blurred in the extreme foreground right.
